[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>It <qex>kythes</qex> bright . . . because all is dark around
it.</q> <rj><qau>Sir W. Scott.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

